\[\mathbf{Reg}_{\text{\tiny DM}}(T) \geq\frac{T}{2}\cdot\left(\max_{\overline{M}\in\mathcal{M}^{+}} \mathsf{r}\text{-}\mathsf{dec}^{\mathsf{c}}_{\underline{\varepsilon}(T)}( \mathcal{M}\cup\{\overline{M}\},\overline{M})-4C_{\tau}\underline{\varepsilon} (T)\right)-1\] \[\geq\frac{T}{2}\cdot\left(\mathsf{r}\text{-}\mathsf{dec}^{ \mathsf{c}}_{\underline{\varepsilon}(T)}(\mathcal{M})-4C_{\tau}\underline{ \varepsilon}(T)\right)-1\]

